org.qcri.rheem.core.optimizer.enumeration

Class PlanEnumeration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.qcri.rheem.core.optimizer.enumeration.PlanEnumeration

  • public class PlanEnumeration
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a collection of PlanImplementations that all implement the same section of a RheemPlan (which is assumed to contain OperatorAlternatives in general).

    Instances can be mutated and combined in algebraic manner. In particular, instances can be unioned if they implement the same part of the RheemPlan, concatenated if there are contact points, and pruned.
